description: portrait of Diana with light brown curly hair in an updo with some loose curls in front, wearing a gold and silver headdress, earrings with clear drops and an armlet with a large green gem and pearls; figure is bare-breasted and wears a pinkish-red garment and holds a spear on a staff with a pinkish-red tassel
marks: Signature and Date ULQ, in grey: [CH. 1607.]
title: Diana as Goddess of the Hunt
